						<summary>

						<p>This is fragmentary. It mentions the village Jinēndramaṅgalam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kuruvaḍimidi••••• in Muttūṟṟu-kūṟṟam and the god Arha-Paramēśvara Māḷuvanāyakar, and records some gift (of land and money) to the temple. Two other pieces mention a <hi rend="italic">kāvaṟ-chuvandiram.</hi> </p>						

